## Cleaning

```bash
# Clean build artifacts
rm -rf build tmp

# Clean cloned git repositories (openembedded-core, bitbake, etc.)
./rm_git_repos.sh

# Clean Docker image
docker rmi yocto-ubuntu:24.04
```

## .gitignore

The following directories are automatically generated by Kas and should be ignored:
- `build/` - build output
- `tmp/` - temporary build files
- `sstate-cache/` - shared state cache
- `downloads/` - downloaded sources
- `bitbake/` - BitBake tool
- `openembedded-core/` - OpenEmbedded Core layer
- `meta-raspberrypi/` - Raspberry Pi BSP layer
- `meta-poky/` - Poky distribution layer
